title: Vanilla OnePlus 10 could launch with 150W wired fast charging support
content:
After launching its latest flagship — the OnePlus 10 Pro — in international markets last month, OnePlus might be gearing up to launch the vanilla OnePlus 10. Although the company hasn’t shared any official information about the device so far, renowned leaker OnLeaks has now revealed its specifications. According to OnLeaks (via Digit), OnePlus is currently testing two variants

The post Vanilla OnePlus 10 could launch with 150W wired fast charging support appeared first on xda-developers.
description: A new leak about the upcoming OnePlus 10 suggests that it could launch with either a Qualcomm or a MediaTek chipset.
